 of the Year]] (shortlisted): 2005\u201306.<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/2335663/Why-the-writers-voted-for-a-safe-pair-of-hands.html | title=Why the writers voted for a safe pair of hands | newspaper=[[Daily Telegraph|Telegraph]] | date=21 April 2006 | accessdate=12 May 2019}}</ref>\n* [[Scottish Premier League monthly awards|Scottish Premier League Player of the Month]] (3): [[2005\u201306 Scottish Premier League#Monthly awards|November 2005]], [[2005\u201306 Scottish Premier League#Monthly awards|January 2006]], [[2009\u201310 Scottish Premier League#Monthly awards|December 2009]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/r/rangers/8461272.stm |title=Walter Smith and Kris Boyd rewarded for Rangers form |date=15 January 2010|work=BBC Sport |accessdate=15 January 2010}}</ref>\n* [[List of Scottish Professional Football League monthly award winners|Scottish Premiership Player of the Month]]: December 2017<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/42692369 |title=Kilmarnock: Kris Boyd and Steve Clarke win December awards |work=BBC Sport |publisher=BBC |date=15 January 2018 |accessdate=15 January 2018}}</ref>\n* [[List of Scottish Premier League monthly award winners|Scottish Premier League Young Player of the Month]] (2): August 2002,<ref name=\"young player\"/> January 2003<ref>{{cite news|title=Boyd surprised at award|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/k/kilmarnock/2730831.stm|work=BBC Sport|date=13 February 2003|accessdate=21 July 2016}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category}}\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20140903063034/http://www.rangers.co.uk/teams/first-team/item/7529-kris-boyd Rangers F.C. profile]\n*{{SFA profile}}\n*{{Soccerbase}}\n{{Navboxes colour\n|bg=gold\n|fg=navy\n|bordercolor=navy\n|title= Awards\n|list1=\n{{SPL topscorers}}\n{{2006\u201307 PFA Scotland SPL Team of the Year}}\n{{2009\u201310 PFA Scotland SPL Team of the