5 January 2010}}</ref>\n* [[List of Scottish Professional Football League monthly award winners|Scottish Premiership Player of the Month]]: December 2017<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/42692369 |title=Kilmarnock: Kris Boyd and Steve Clarke win December awards |work=BBC Sport |publisher=BBC |date=15 January 2018 |accessdate=15 January 2018}}</ref>\n* [[List of Scottish Premier League monthly award winners|Scottish Premier League Young Player of the Month]] (2): August 2002,<ref name=\"young player\"/> January 2003<ref>{{cite news|title=Boyd surprised at award|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/k/kilmarnock/2730831.stm|work=BBC Sport|date=13 February 2003|accessdate=21 July 2016}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category}}\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20140903063034/http://www.rangers.co.uk/teams/first-team/item/7529-kris-boyd Rangers F.C. profile]\n*{{SFA profile}}\n*{{Soccerbase}}\n{{Navboxes colour\n|bg=gold\n|fg=navy\n|bordercolor=navy\n|title= Awards\n|list1=\n{{SPL topscorers}}\n{{2006\u201307 PFA Scotland SPL Team of the Year}}\n{{2009\u201310 PFA Scotland SPL Team of the Year}}\n{{2013\u201314 PFA Scotland Scottish Premiership Team of the Year}}\n{{2017\u201318 PFA Scotland Scottish Premiership Team of the Year}}\n}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Boyd, Kris}}\n[[Category:1983 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Irvine, North Ayrshire]]\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n[[Category:Scottish footballers]]\n[[Category:Scottish expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Scottish expatriate sportspeople in Turkey]]\n[[Category:Scottish expatriate sportspeople in the United States]]\n[[Category:Scotland international footballers]]\n[[Category:Scotland B international footballers]]\n[[Category:Scotland under-21 international footballers]]\n[[Category:Scottish Premier League players]]\n[[Category:English Football League players]]\n[[Category:Kilmarnock F.C. players]