ogna]]\n|-\n|1974\u201375<br />''Details''\n|{{flagicon|URS|1955|size=30px}} <br> [[VC Radiotechnik|Elektrotechnika]]\n|Group Stage\n|{{flagicon|BUL|1971|size=30px}} <br> [[Levski Volley|Levski-Spartak]]\n|{{flagicon|TCH|size=30px}} <br> [[VK Kladno|Aero Odolena Voda]]\n|{{flagicon|HUN|size=30px}} <br> [[\u00dajpesti TE|\u00dajpesti]]\n|-\n|1975\u201376<br />''Details''\n|{{flagicon|BUL|1971|size=30px}} <br> [[VC CSKA Sofia|CSKA Sofia]]\n|Group Stage\n|{{flagicon|TCH|size=30px}} <br> [[VKP Bratislava|\u010cerven\u00e1 hv\u011bzda Bratislava]]\n|{{flagicon|ITA|size=30px}} <br> [[CUS Torino Pallavolo|Klippan Torino]]\n|{{flagicon|NED|size=30px}} <br> Bouwlust Orawi\n|-\n|1976\u201377<br />''Details''\n|{{flagicon|URS|1955|size=30px}} <br> [[VC Radiotechnik|Elektrotechnika]]\n|Group Stage\n|{{flagicon|ROM|1965|size=30px}} <br> [[CSA Steaua Bucure\u015fti|Steaua Bucure\u015fti]]\n|{{flagicon|TCH|size=30px}} <br> [[VK Kladno|Aero Odolena Voda]]\n|{{flagicon|HUN|size=30px}} <br> Budapest Honv\u00e9d\n|-\n|1977\u201378<br />''Details''\n|{{flagicon|TCH|size=30px}} <br> [[PVK Olymp Praha|Rud\u00e1 Hv\u011bzda Praha]]\n|Group Stage\n|{{flagicon|POL|1928|size=30px}} <br> [[Indykpol AZS Olsztyn|AZS Olsztyn]]\n|{{flagicon|ITA|size=30px}} <br> Paoletti Catania\n|{{flagicon|TUR|size=30px}} <br> Eczac\u0131ba\u015f\u0131\n|-\n|1978\u201379<br />''Details''\n|{{flagicon|ROM|1965|size=30px}} <br> [[CS Dinamo Bucure\u0219ti (volleyball)|Dinamo Bucure\u015fti]]\n|Group Stage\n|{{flagicon|BUL|1971|size=30px}} <br> [[Levski Volley|Levski-Spartak]]\n|{{flagicon|TCH|size=30px}} <br> [[PVK Olymp Praha|Rud\u00e1 hv\u011bzda Praha]]\n|{{flagicon|NED|size=30px}} <br> Gemeenteserv Vught\n|-\n|1979\u201380<br />''Details''\n|{{flagicon|ITA|size=30px}} <br> [[Modena Volley|Panini Modena]]\n|Group Stage\n|{{flagicon|GRC|size=30px}} <br> [[Panathinaikos V.C.|Panathinaikos]]\n|{{flagicon|TCH|size=30px}} <br> [[VK Kladno|Aero Odolena Voda]]\n|{{flagicon|TUR|size=30px}} <br> Vinilex Istanbul\n|-\n|19